headline.print_headline: Red Bull's F1 Test Nightmare Continues
headline.main: Red Bull's F1 Test Nightmare Continues

lead_paragraph: Red Bull designer Adrian Newey went back to his drawing board on Thursday after another nightmare day for the Formula One champions in pre-season testing in southern Spain.
